{"tid":1612401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實可唔可以請聯合國UN部隊黎鎮壓黑警","createTime":"2019-10-02T08:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T10:00:42.000Z","uid":20430,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0c34d1b59d81485dd73e50e00ab5ee4932199e4d","tid":1612401,"uid":20430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"聯合國維持和平部隊<br />\n<br />\n說明聯合國維持和平部隊簡稱聯合國維和部隊，指由大會或聯合國安全理事會至少需九票贊成核准部署並決定其任務授權的部隊，此部隊只配備簡單武器用以自衛和維持秩序之用途。秘書長對於如何發起和開展行動必須提出建議並報告其進展情況，而維持和平部隊的行動部則負責各維和部隊的日常行政指導，管理和後勤支援。 維基百科<br />\n<br />\n有無辦法叫佢地黎"},{"pid":"33dbe7c1697c453311369feb7fb4f0d14fd0ac28","tid":1612401,"uid":277235,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:47:27.000Z","msg":"UＮ　入面有個恐怖主義国家"},{"pid":"68e26b1878dd9ddf9b75a2e531ea699f0b97cb9f","tid":1612401,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"都係佢啲人"},{"pid":"653a9b7da10f9db336a8f2164aa817972d96f68f","tid":1612401,"uid":300655,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:48:05.000Z","msg":"支那一票否決已經可以收皮 好似係"},{"pid":"28711cc564c2d8ff7c25f7a5cf83ff6fcc188f6a","tid":1612401,"uid":127177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:49:02.000Z","msg":"叫北約好似會快D"},{"pid":"8468bc9b7445e521f8e5553fc0f51f16451e55d0","tid":1612401,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:50:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0f33c91da3ed8b4937d9e83df4084b2f6b7b314","tid":1612401,"uid":42740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:53:08.000Z","msg":"UN有兩個痴線國家係常任<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b48157cb8c4ef73cc74fc509a7f6393ec5051c1","tid":1612401,"uid":269465,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"你地真係好撚幼稚.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji